<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>人生</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify"><strong>文\草根一一</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">小时候</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">想长大的模样</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">长大后</p>
<p class="ql-align-justify">想回归故乡</p>            <div class="lookall-box">
